<i>adverb</i>: 허다히 [허다히], 풍족히 [풍조키], 풍성히 [풍성히], 푸짐히 [푸짐히], 듬뿍 [듬뿍], 담뿍 [담뿍], 넉넉히 [넝너키] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허다히 [허다히]</dt><br>
<dd>countlessly; so many; plentifully</dd><br>
<dd>수가 매우 많게.</dd><br>
<dd>In great numbers.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍족히 [풍조키]</dt><br>
<dd>abundantly; plentifully; richly</dd><br>
<dd>매우 넉넉해서 부족함이 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>In enough and ample quantity, without a shortage.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풍성히 [풍성히]</dt><br>
<dd>abundantly; plentifully; amply</dd><br>
<dd>넉넉하고 많이.</dd><br>
<dd>In plenty, in an abundant quantity.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸짐히 [푸짐히]</dt><br>
<dd>plentifully; abundantly; generously</dd><br>
<dd>마음이 흐뭇하도록 넉넉하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In an ample quantity, to one's satisfaction.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>듬뿍 [듬뿍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. to the brim</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 넘칠 정도로 수북이 가득한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In such large amounts that something is about to overflow.</dd><br>
<dd>2. much; plentifully</dd><br>
<dd>아주 많거나 넉넉한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A lot or enough.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>담뿍 [담뿍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. to the brim</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것이 넘칠 정도로 소복이 가득한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In such an amount that something is about to overflow.</dd><br>
<dd>2. much; plentifully</dd><br>
<dd>많거나 넉넉한 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In large or sufficient amounts.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>넉넉히 [넝너키]</dt><br>
<dd>1. sufficiently; plentifully</dd><br>
<dd>크기나 수 등이 적거나 부족하지 않고 충분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being enough, neither too small nor insufficient in size or number.</dd><br>
<dd>2. wealthily; richly</dd><br>
<dd>살림이 부족하지 않고 여유 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being well off.</dd><br>
<dd>3. fully</dd><br>
<dd>가능성 등이 충분하게.</dd><br>
<dd>With enough possibility.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>